 solar interior and argue that a potentially important\nmechanism for mixing in Main Sequence stars has so far been neglected.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Jun 2009 18:58:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
