. asymptotic to\n$(5/9)D(\\epsilon,n)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jun 2009 02:28:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Aug 2010 05:16:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-08-16"}
